I did something a little bit differently on this one.  I added a sweep  
kill switch on the back.  The sweep was draining the batteries even though  the 
radio wasn&#39;t on, so i added a switch to kill the power when not in  use.  
Popping a battery out will do the same thing, but this is a lot  neater.

Here is the test audio on both bands, i don&#39;t think they like my boxes or  
the sweep.  Just listen to my sample files i pulled out.  

